</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-059355DA-2D5F-4D71-BE7B-24CE99CD6E66" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Functional logging (if available)</title><p class="- topic/p ">No logging available which can pinpoint to this case. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-D7132266-4290-4FFC-8E55-65707F81A68F" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">ADAM-triggers</title><p class="- topic/p ">No available ADAM-triggers 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-1F811B47-7AF2-413F-9C26-26DD568D6853" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-9F69D5F1-4C3C-472D-A6B2-EAE8953B4546-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9F69D5F1-4C3C-472D-A6B2-EAE8953B4546-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the pollution is only visible in the first 50 cm of a new loaded media roll 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Use “cut long strip” option when loading new media 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D076FF1A-9118-474A-A96B-1BA36F0F7B7D" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-16FA1E88-D905-4900-9724-49F3B56B5A4D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-16FA1E88-D905-4900-9724-49F3B56B5A4D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if the media is polluted 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean a part of the media using Isopropyl Alcohol. If this prevents the presence of artifacts use other media 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean media drawer 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean the media drawer including the rollers. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Clean X-tran rollers 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Perform manual maintenance to make sure the matrix plate and the downside of the printhead carriage is clean. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Don’t use the option “Advanced nozzle optimalisation” 
</p><fig id="GUID-1B3C53FA-8C08-4DE4-B2DD-A2DEEAA3BAFF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DBB4E8D6-212C-42F2-9894-9F612F35C917-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DBB4E8D6-212C-42F2-9894-9F612F35C917-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Is the pollution present on static media ? 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Use other batch or roll 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install MOD39 (1070123271) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Store media in a clean environment. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Maintain the engine according to the “Care and use”-poster 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Use “Cut long strip” when loading new media 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Install MOD39 in case of static media. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">Pollution on the media during printing will cause encapsulation of the pollution into the ink layer. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> In most cases the pollution is limited to the first 50 cm of the print. In those cases the media isn’t stored in a clean environment and the outside to the roll is polluted. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After cutting a long strip, the pollution is removed, ensuring that the remaining printed media is free from contamination.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Pollution during printing also appears when static media is used in a polluted environment. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">There is a special MOD-kit (39) available to prevent static build-up during printing. 
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-945E6C60-1212-47DF-9487-92374227D4B4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
